des: Interested in Mathematics? Wanna know what is happening in Math world. Ask Math conference calendar and attend events to get better understanding! Math is a subject that makes kids either jump for joy or rip their hair out. But, Math is needed for almost every single profession in the world. So, encourage others to participate in conferences.
